# ── Build artifacts (will be regenerated inside the image) ──────────────────
**/.next/
**/.turbo/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/coverage/
**/.cache/

# ── Dependencies (installed fresh per stage) ────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules/

# ── Source control ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.github/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# ── Local dev / OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.log
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp

# ── Environment / secrets (NEVER bake into images) ──────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
.claude/

# ── Docker-related (avoid recursion) ────────────────────────────────────────
Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore

# ── Editor / project metadata ───────────────────────────────────────────────
*.md
!README.md
LICENSE
.editorconfig
.prettier*
.eslintcache

# ── Tests / fixtures (typically not needed in production runner) ────────────
**/__tests__/
**/__mocks__/
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx

# ── Claude Code / scratch ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
